  steps:
  - image: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 9568d4317c3349147921404078269b34, type: 3}
    title: Health
    description: The red bar indicates the current and max health. If health reaches
      0 on the hero you lose the game and you have to start over! If an ally or enemy
      health reaches 0 then they get destroyed and removed from the game!
  - image: {fileID: 0}
    title: Shield
    description: The blue bar indicates the shield you currently have. Shield will
      block the damage received first. If you have no more shield then you will lose
      health instead. Shield gets removed every turn!
  - image: {fileID: 0}
    title: Armor
    description: The orange bar indicates the armor you currently have. Armor take
      priority over health and Shield and it is permanent for the remaining of the
      Combat!
